'''欧内斯特·莫尼兹'''（Ernest Jeffrey Moniz，1944年12月22日-）是一名美国[[核物理|核物理]]学家，自2013年5月起任[[美国能源部长|美国能源部长]]<ref name="weiner">{{cite news|last=Weiner|first=Rachel|title=Ernest Moniz confirmed as Energy secretary|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/post-politics/wp/2013/05/16/ernest-moniz-confirmed-as-energy-secretary/|accessdate=16 May 2013|newspaper=Washington Post|date=16 May 2013|archive-date=2013-06-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130601153841/http://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/post-politics/wp/2013/05/16/ernest-moniz-confirmed-as-energy-secretary/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。之前在1995到1997年担任[[比尔·克林顿|比尔·克林顿]]政府的科技政策办公室的助理主管<ref>{{cite web | url =http://www.csmonitor.com/Environment/Energy-Voices/2013/0211/Will-Ernest-Moniz-be-the-next-Energy-secretary | title =Will Ernest Moniz be the next Energy secretary? | publisher =''[[Christian_Science_Monitor|Christian Science Monitor]]'' | author =David J. Unger | date =February 11, 2013 | accessdate =February 24, 2013 | archive-date =2013-07-13 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20130713000543/http://www.csmonitor.com/Environment/Energy-Voices/2013/0211/Will-Ernest-Moniz-be-the-next-Energy-secretary | dead-url =no }}</ref>，1997到2001年在[[美国能源部|美国能源部]]任职<ref>{{cite web | url =http://www.nationaljournal.com/energy/who-is-ernest-moniz-obama-s-likely-pick-for-energy-secretary-20130221 | title =Who Is Ernest Moniz, Obama's Likely Pick for Energy Secretary? | publisher =nationaljournal.com | author =Niraj Chokshi | date =February 21, 2013 | accessdate =February 24, 2013 | archive-date =2013-02-24 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20130224071809/http://www.nationaljournal.com/energy/who-is-ernest-moniz-obama-s-likely-pick-for-energy-secretary-20130221 | dead-url =no }}</ref>。

他是非盈利的能源研究机构''The Cyprus Institute''和''Cecil and Ida Green Professor of Physics and Engineering Systems''的创始成员和主管，以及[[麻省理工学院|麻省理工学院]]的能源与环境实验室主任<ref>{{cite web | url =http://esd.mit.edu/Faculty_Pages/moniz/moniz.htm | title =Faculty & Teaching Staff | publisher =[[MIT_Engineering_Systems_Division|MIT Engineering Systems Division]] | author =''[[Massachusetts_Institute_of_Technology|Massachusetts Institute of Technology]]'' | date = | accessdate =February 24, 2013 | archive-date =2012-02-02 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20120202050820/http://esd.mit.edu/Faculty_Pages/moniz/moniz.htm | dead-url =no }}</ref>。 

==早年==
他的父母是来自于[[葡萄牙|葡萄牙]][[聖米格爾島|聖米格爾島]]的移民，他生于[[马萨诸塞州|马萨诸塞州]]的[[福尔里弗_(马萨诸塞州)|福尔里弗]]<ref>{{cite web | url =http://ojornal.com/portuguese-brazilian-news/2013/03/obama-to-name-portuguese-american-scientist-to-head-energy-department/#axzz2Mf74deOw | title =Obama to name Fall River Native to head Energy Department | publisher =ojornal.com | author = | year =2013 | accessdate =March 5, 2013 | archive-date =2013-07-29 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20130729004942/http://ojornal.com/portuguese-brazilian-news/2013/03/obama-to-name-portuguese-american-scientist-to-head-energy-department/#axzz2Mf74deOw | dead-url =no }}</ref>。

1966年取得[[波士頓學院|波士頓學院]]的[[物理学|物理学]]学位，后来又于1972年获得[[史丹佛大學|史丹佛大學]]的[[理论物理学|理论物理学]][[博士|博士]]学位<ref>{{cite web | url =http://www.bc.edu/content/bc/alumni/news/BCM/previous_bcm/moniz.html | title =Advancement News Spring 2009 | publisher =bc.edu | author =''[[Boston_College|Boston College]]'' | year =2009 | accessdate =February 24, 2013 | deadurl =yes | archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20130402085439/http://www.bc.edu/content/bc/alumni/news/BCM/previous_bcm/moniz.html | archivedate =2013年4月2日 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url =http://gcep.stanford.edu/events/symposium/symposium2005/keynote.html | title =Events GCEP Research Symposium 2005 Keynote Speakers Prof. Freeman Dyson Prof. Ernest Moniz Prof. David Victor | publisher =stanford.edu | year =2005 | accessdate =February 24, 2013 | archive-date =2013-10-14 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20131014163411/http://gcep.stanford.edu/events/symposium/symposium2005/keynote.html | dead-url =no }}</ref>。1973年他成为[[麻省理工学院|麻省理工学院]]的物理学教师。

